{"type": "article", "id": 17268, "title": "泰迪熊版的Instapump Fury", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-09T07:10:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 105, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134514WYvhaNsk5pbrygMV.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t洛杉矶球鞋店 BAIT 与 Reebok 曾联名多个鞋款，这一次他们以今年6月上映的电影《泰迪熊2》为灵感，重新打造经典款 Instapump Fury。鞋身是浅棕色的，带有大面积的绒毛和麂皮。鞋背上有一个凸起来的熊鼻子，形象地指向了泰迪熊，很俏皮。鞋后跟上画了泰迪熊的脸和 BAIT 标志，让这款原本很有未来感的鞋变得活泼，喜欢泰迪熊的人一定不忘收藏，售价 170 美元，<a href=\"http://www.baitme.com/bait-ted2-reebok\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144404TwidxHQqsZznOREX.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144405RDIdgUuS2ozACcx7.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144405lJgUTydkFKBurfZY.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144406kJ8D9CShaI6j5fzt.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"416\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.55466667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}